00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:19,200
Limpy

2
00:01:19,879 --> 00:01:21,359
If I go all out,

3
00:01:22,079 --> 00:01:23,519
I won't be able to control myself.

4
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:25,120
When my strength runs out,

5
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:27,280
remember to take me with you.

6
00:01:27,879 --> 00:01:29,280
No need to go that hard.

7
00:01:30,280 --> 00:01:31,560
Since when do people from Black Street

8
00:01:32,120 --> 00:01:33,760
start putting their lives

9
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:35,599
in other people's hands?

10
00:01:39,519 --> 00:01:40,680
Old Gu,

11
00:01:41,079 --> 00:01:43,959
your temper hasn't changed a bit.

12
00:01:46,719 --> 00:01:48,599
Always picking on the weak.

13
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:54,079
You're here.

14
00:01:55,680 --> 00:01:56,519
Then I'll go take a breather.

15
00:01:56,519 --> 00:01:57,120
Go on.

16
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:03,840
You old geezer,

17
00:02:04,159 --> 00:02:05,280
why are you here too?

18
00:02:05,439 --> 00:02:06,599
My son is here.

19
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:08,039
Of course I had to come.

20
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:09,800
Let's get out of here.

21
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:11,120
If we stay any longer,

22
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:12,639
this old geezer's gonna drop dead from rage.

23
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,960
You and your son can leave.

24
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:18,039
But they

25
00:02:18,560 --> 00:02:19,639
have to stay here.

26
00:02:20,319 --> 00:02:21,080
After all,

27
00:02:21,439 --> 00:02:22,719
the Imperial Capital

28
00:02:23,319 --> 00:02:25,120
isn't a place just anyone can mess with.

29
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,159
Uncle Gu,

30
00:02:32,639 --> 00:02:34,199
these are Shanhai City's people.

31
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:35,240
We have to leave together.

32
00:02:36,479 --> 00:02:37,439
Young man,

33
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:38,800
some matters

34
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:41,080
aren't for you to meddle in.

35
00:02:44,479 --> 00:02:45,159
I know.

36
00:02:46,719 --> 00:02:47,680
As a junior, perhaps

37
00:02:48,159 --> 00:02:49,719
I'm not qualified to speak with you.

38
00:02:50,039 --> 00:02:51,439
But at least in this moment,

39
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:53,439
I represent Shanhai City.

40
00:02:54,479 --> 00:02:56,039
As long as they live in Shanhai City,

41
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:58,000
they are our people.

42
00:02:58,759 --> 00:03:00,400
If we can't even protect

43
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,280
our own citizens,

44
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:02,800
then Shanhai City

45
00:03:02,919 --> 00:03:04,599
will lose its very foundation.

46
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:05,919
Wouldn't you agree?

47
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:08,080
Shanhai City can't be insulted,

48
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:10,000
but the Imperial Capital can?

49
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:11,560
If they die here,

50
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:12,639
it all ends.

51
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:13,960
Protect them,

52
00:03:14,159 --> 00:03:15,759
and you won't be leaving either.

53
00:03:16,159 --> 00:03:18,120
If Uncle Gu insists on fighting,

54
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:19,759
then Shanhai City

55
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,639
will oblige you to the very end.

56
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:23,960
Old Liu,

57
00:03:24,159 --> 00:03:25,599
is this your stance too?

58
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:27,159
Help me down, would you?

59
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:29,080
My legs have gone numb.

60
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,439
Sitting on this thing

61
00:03:31,879 --> 00:03:33,159
is uncomfortable.

62
00:03:37,439 --> 00:03:38,319
Old Gu,

63
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:40,800
do you really want to fight?

64
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,879
I admit you're strong,

65
00:03:44,199 --> 00:03:45,520
but the Imperial Capital

66
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:46,599
isn't weak either.

67
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:47,840
Son,

68
00:03:48,879 --> 00:03:51,479
let me show you what your old man can do.

69
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:55,319
Know why they call me Liu Wudi?

70
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:56,680
Because I

71
00:03:56,879 --> 00:03:58,159
am invincible in this era.

72
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,080
Afraid to die?

73
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:10,919
Actually,

74
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,719
I'd like to experience it.

75
00:04:31,519 --> 00:04:33,240
Invincible in this era.

76
00:04:58,160 --> 00:04:59,079
Sword Rain!

77
00:05:15,399 --> 00:05:17,160
What kind of immortal art is this?

78
00:05:17,399 --> 00:05:19,519
That's a character from the MMO Xiankui,

79
00:05:19,519 --> 00:05:20,920
the Gentleman Sword's second skill,

80
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:22,560
unlocked at level 15.

81
00:05:22,879 --> 00:05:23,800
I've played it.

82
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:27,480
Don't tell me what blessed him

83
00:05:27,639 --> 00:05:28,920
was a video game.

84
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:29,639
No.

85
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:32,240
It's just that his immortal spirit power

86
00:05:32,639 --> 00:05:33,639
is overwhelmingly abundant,

87
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:36,800
so he developed his own techniques.

88
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:38,600
In other words,

89
00:05:39,199 --> 00:05:41,560
the rest of us walk the original immortal path,

90
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:42,399
but he

91
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:44,360
has forged a new one.

92
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:46,160
He

93
00:05:46,759 --> 00:05:48,879
is truly cultivating immortality,

94
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:51,040
an immortal path of his own.

95
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:06,199
Nature as essence, spirit as function

96
00:06:06,199 --> 00:06:07,560
Cultivate both to attain the immortal path

97
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:08,839
The human heart is perilous, the Dao heart subtle

98
00:06:08,839 --> 00:06:10,160
Be refined, be one, hold to the mean

99
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:11,639
The human heart is, in essence, the heavenly heart

100
00:06:11,639 --> 00:06:13,319
Human heart is Dao heart, Dao heart is Heaven's heart

101
00:06:13,319 --> 00:06:14,920
Originally one, divided through neglect

102
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:15,759
Thus split into two functions

103
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,680
Liu Wudi's third skill:

104
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:24,759
One Spear Pierces the Heavens!

105
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:42,600
I knew it.

106
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:45,399
All those losses weren't my fault.

107
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:47,720
Used outside, these skills...

108
00:06:47,839 --> 00:06:49,600
they work incredibly well!

109
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,519
My teammates were just trash.

110
00:06:53,079 --> 00:06:54,199
It's not on me.

111
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:56,720
Old Daoist,

112
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:57,519
You holding up?

113
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,560
I've got a few more ideas here.

114
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:00,439
Want to try them?

115
00:07:00,639 --> 00:07:01,319
You up for it?

116
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,279
Brilliant Starlight!

117
00:07:06,319 --> 00:07:08,519
That name alone sounds powerful.

118
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:09,360
What?

119
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:10,399
Let's try again.

120
00:07:11,639 --> 00:07:12,199
Come on.

121
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:18,639
Why is there no damage output?

122
00:07:21,839 --> 00:07:22,519
What the hell?

123
00:07:23,759 --> 00:07:25,120
What went wrong?

124
00:07:25,519 --> 00:07:27,920
I didn't fully replicate the game skill.

125
00:07:28,079 --> 00:07:29,720
Just borrowed the look.

126
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:31,279
Could it be...

127
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:33,000
I'm out of mana?

128
00:07:37,759 --> 00:07:38,480
Old Gu,

129
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,879
How are things on your end?

130
00:07:39,879 --> 00:07:40,800
Can you still fight?

131
00:07:46,439 --> 00:07:47,800
Compared to back then,

132
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:49,360
you've gotten stronger.

133
00:07:49,759 --> 00:07:50,680
Not too shabby.

134
00:07:51,279 --> 00:07:52,839
I remember as kids,

135
00:07:53,279 --> 00:07:55,240
I beat you spoiled young masters

136
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:57,199
till you didn't even dare look me in the eye.

137
00:07:57,439 --> 00:07:58,439
Now that we're grown,

138
00:07:58,680 --> 00:08:00,040
it should be the same.

139
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:03,519
I remember one time,

140
00:08:03,959 --> 00:08:05,519
I dragged you into the bathroom...

141
00:08:05,519 --> 00:08:06,079
Shut up!

142
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:08,480
Today,

143
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:10,639
what you and I represent

144
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,360
are the Imperial Capital

145
00:08:12,839 --> 00:08:14,079
and Shanhai City.

146
00:08:14,439 --> 00:08:16,240
This pointless nonsense

147
00:08:16,439 --> 00:08:17,600
needs to stop.

148
00:08:18,639 --> 00:08:19,959
I'll ask you just one thing.

149
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:21,839
Is Shanhai City

150
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:25,160
ready to go to war with the Imperial Capital?

151
00:08:25,519 --> 00:08:26,399
No, no, no.

152
00:08:26,759 --> 00:08:28,439
Shanhai City can't beat the Imperial Capital.

153
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:29,680
In that case,

154
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:32,240
why do you dare provoke me?

155
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:35,639
Shanhai City can't beat the Imperial Capital,

156
00:08:35,639 --> 00:08:36,879
but I can beat you.

157
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:37,919
I guarantee

158
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:39,879
no matter who stands in front of you,

159
00:08:40,759 --> 00:08:42,519
from this distance,

160
00:08:42,559 --> 00:08:43,360
I can kill you.

161
00:08:57,320 --> 00:08:58,600
So sign a written guarantee

162
00:08:58,960 --> 00:08:59,799
to make it official:

163
00:09:00,279 --> 00:09:01,639
These troublemakers

164
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:03,600
will be taken back to Shanhai City for handling.

165
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:05,679
Everything that happened at the Imperial Capital

166
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:08,600
has nothing to do with Shanhai City.

167
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:12,080
Are you threatening me?

168
00:09:12,080 --> 00:09:12,720
That's right.

169
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,559
I am threatening you.

170
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:15,799
Will you sign it or not?

171
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:21,000
Waters of the Heavenly River!

172
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:25,000
Dark clouds press down, the city about to fall!

173
00:09:47,799 --> 00:09:49,519
Look, you got it all dirty.

174
00:09:49,519 --> 00:09:50,399
Chengfeng, quick, quick.

175
00:09:50,559 --> 00:09:51,200
Come on.

176
00:09:51,879 --> 00:09:53,200
That Uncle Gu of yours,

177
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,200
he's getting on in years.

178
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,759
Can't even hold a notebook steady.

179
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:00,960
I'll wait for Shanhai City's word

180
00:10:01,360 --> 00:10:03,480
on how they handle that crew.

181
00:10:08,879 --> 00:10:09,440
Let's go.

182
00:10:11,519 --> 00:10:12,440
Let's see how he wrote it.

183
00:10:14,039 --> 00:10:14,720
No problem.

184
00:10:16,559 --> 00:10:18,440
He just left like that?

185
00:10:20,279 --> 00:10:22,759
Don't let his pathetic act fool you.

186
00:10:23,679 --> 00:10:25,320
This guy is rotten to the core.

187
00:10:26,399 --> 00:10:28,200
As long as I don't actually kill him,

188
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:30,440
he'll always find a way to stab me in the back.

189
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:34,240
Now that he knows my true strength,

190
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:37,399
he won't give me another chance

191
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:39,159
to get close to him.

192
00:10:40,679 --> 00:10:42,639
No matter how strong a person is,

193
00:10:42,759 --> 00:10:44,000
they still fear a scumbag.

194
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:48,200
Wonder which cities they'll screw over this time.

195
00:10:49,039 --> 00:10:52,080
At least Shanhai City won't get caught up in it.

196
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:54,240
That's good enough.

197
00:10:55,519 --> 00:10:56,879
That's good enough.

198
00:11:06,879 --> 00:11:07,600
Gentlemen,

199
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:09,600
any other thoughts?

200
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:12,440
He still owes Black Street two lives.

201
00:11:14,080 --> 00:11:15,480
More than two people died

202
00:11:15,639 --> 00:11:17,240
in the Imperial Capital.

203
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:20,879
Forget it.

204
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:22,720
Mark it down in the ledger.

205
00:11:23,559 --> 00:11:24,799
We'll collect when the chance comes.

206
00:11:25,159 --> 00:11:26,159
Regardless,

207
00:11:26,279 --> 00:11:27,799
we have to give Old Gu some face.

208
00:11:29,399 --> 00:11:31,120
Black Street will close down for two years.

209
00:11:31,240 --> 00:11:32,120
Any objections?

210
00:11:42,879 --> 00:11:43,559
None here.

211
00:11:44,879 --> 00:11:45,759
Then it's settled.

212
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:46,960
Once we reopen,

213
00:11:48,200 --> 00:11:50,000
if you try to kill anyone in Shanhai City,

214
00:11:51,039 --> 00:11:52,639
I'll still step in.

215
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:54,960
Xiaofeng, let's go.

216
00:11:55,639 --> 00:11:56,440
You go on ahead.

217
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:57,519
I've got something to take care of.

218
00:11:58,480 --> 00:11:59,120
Alright then.

219
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:05,159
Why does he think we enjoy killing?

220
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:07,320
I'm sick of it already.

221
00:12:08,919 --> 00:12:10,320
Tongtong doesn't like it.

222
00:12:11,799 --> 00:12:14,120
I can recite ten full Buddhist scriptures

223
00:12:14,240 --> 00:12:16,600
on the virtues of peace and kindness.

224
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:19,159
You know that stuff too?

225
00:12:19,679 --> 00:12:20,679
Just a little.

226
00:13:10,919 --> 00:13:11,480
Let's go.

227
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:44,240
Mission accomplished.

228
00:13:54,399 --> 00:13:55,120
Ladies and gentlemen,

229
00:13:55,360 --> 00:13:57,039
Master Mao's press conference

230
00:13:57,039 --> 00:13:58,720
for "Above the Immortals"

231
00:13:58,840 --> 00:14:00,240
is now officially beginning.

232
00:14:00,360 --> 00:14:04,000
Alright, alright, alright.

233
00:14:05,720 --> 00:14:06,480
Hello.

234
00:14:06,639 --> 00:14:08,519
This manga is incredibly popular right now.

235
00:14:08,639 --> 00:14:10,519
The redemption and emotion throughout

236
00:14:10,519 --> 00:14:12,039
have moved us deeply.

237
00:14:12,120 --> 00:14:12,840
I'd like to ask,

238
00:14:12,840 --> 00:14:14,559
under what circumstances did you

239
00:14:14,559 --> 00:14:16,519
get the inspiration for this manga?

240
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:21,799
First of all,

241
00:14:22,679 --> 00:14:26,120
thank you all for loving this work.

242
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:29,120
As for the question

243
00:14:29,480 --> 00:14:30,639
about my inspiration,

244
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:33,039
it's because

245
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:34,759
one day,

246
00:14:35,919 --> 00:14:37,559
I saw a brother and sister

247
00:14:38,639 --> 00:14:39,639
walking down the street.

248
00:14:40,080 --> 00:14:41,799
The sister was gravely ill, beyond cure.

249
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:44,120
The brother carried her on his back,

250
00:14:44,279 --> 00:14:45,600
seeking doctors and medicine all the way.

251
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:48,639
Even when faced with cruel fate,

252
00:14:49,879 --> 00:14:52,240
even facing such injustice in life,

253
00:14:52,799 --> 00:14:54,240
they never abandoned each other.

254
00:14:56,799 --> 00:14:58,039
The brother protected his sister.

255
00:14:58,039 --> 00:14:59,159
The sister cared deeply for her brother.

256
00:14:59,759 --> 00:15:02,159
They were each other's warmest support.

257
00:15:02,759 --> 00:15:04,360
On their faces, there was a kind of...

258
00:15:06,799 --> 00:15:07,879
a kind of smile.

259
00:15:07,879 --> 00:15:09,360
A smile I had never seen before

260
00:15:09,360 --> 00:15:10,279
in my entire life.

261
00:15:11,279 --> 00:15:12,480
And in that very moment,

262
00:15:13,320 --> 00:15:14,679
I felt that this smile

263
00:15:14,960 --> 00:15:16,879
could heal everything in this world.

264
00:15:53,320 --> 00:15:54,200
The seed

265
00:15:54,320 --> 00:15:55,840
has already bloomed.

266
00:15:56,360 --> 00:15:57,320
Now,

267
00:15:57,879 --> 00:15:59,720
it's your turn to take the stage.

